</list><p>Daennie sæjrosne maahtah retorihken bïjre lohkedh jïh lïeredh.</p>
<p>Martin Luther King Jr. at March on Washington</p>
<p><em type="italic">Martin Luther King h </em><em type="italic">åalemem vuelielisnie höölti jaepien 1963, gosse sov minngemes, heskies gæmhpoem ellies årroje-reaktaj bïjre gæmhpoeji afro-amerihkeridie USA:sne. Dïhte aktede vuetjiejistie båvvalgi 1968. Håaleme dan åehpies guktie joekoen daamtaj mubpesth jeahtasåvva, jïh symboline åtnasåvva dan gæmhpose sïerredamme almetji reaktaj åvteste. </em></p>
<p>I have a dream that one day this nation will rise up and live out the true meaning of its creed: ‘We hold these truths to be self-evident, that all men are created equal.'</p>
<p>I have a dream that one day on the red hills of Georgia, the sons of former slaves and the sons of former slave owners will be able to sit down together at the table of brotherhood.</p>
<p>I have a dream that one day, even the state of Mississippi, a desert sweltering with the heat of injustice, sweltering with the heat of oppression, will turn into an oasis of freedom and justice.</p>
<p>I have a dream that my four little children will one day live in a nation where they will not be judged by the color of their skin but by the content of their character.</p>
<p>I have a dream today!</p>
<p>Mannasinie daate håaleme dan åehpies sjïdteme? Magkeres rovnegs faamoe daejtie baakojde dan sjïere dorje? Magkeres daajroe gååvnese daan veele jïh nænnoes dïjren duekesne? Akte taleente mejnie reakadamme, jallh akte veele ussjedamme strategije håalemasse? Nov sån gåabpatjahkh. Martin Luther King ij lij ajve akte tjiehpies håalije, dïhte lij akte retorihke-mïestere. Retorihke lea learoe guktie maahta mubpide jaehkiehtidh. Martin Luther King dam darjoeji gosse tjaebpieslaakan jïh eensilaakan sov goltelæjjide håaloeji. Dïhte lyhkesi dan åvteste veele daajroem teeman bïjre utni, jïh aaj goltelæjjaj jïh tsiehkien bïjre gusnie edtji håaledh.</p>
<p><em type="italic">Retorihke </em>lea learoe håaleme-kåansten bïjre; greeklaanten gïeleste rhetoriké téchne, ”håaleme-tjiehpiesvoete, håaleme-kåanste”. </p>
